                    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-[28px] font-normal text-[#004A86]">
                        Healthcare Professionals Registry (HPR)
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-lg text-[#5A5A5A] leading-relaxed mt-2">
                        The Healthcare Professionals Registry (HPR), a key initiative under ABDM, is a comprehensive digital repository of healthcare professionals across modern and traditional medicine in India. Enrolling in HPR enables professionals to seamlessly integrate into India’s digital health ecosystem, enhancing accessibility, efficiency, and care quality. This centralized directory ensures verified access to skilled professionals for patients and healthcare providers. HPR also improves interoperability, connecting professionals with health facilities, digital records, and government initiatives, fostering a transparent, patient-centric healthcare system.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        
            <div class="mt-24 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-[28px] font-normal text-[#004A86]">
                        Health Facility Registry (HFR)
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-lg text-[#5A5A5A] leading-relaxed mt-2">
                        The Health Facility Registry (HFR) is a comprehensive digital repository that includes both private and public healthcare facilities across India, such as clinics, hospitals, diagnostic labs, imaging centers, and pharmacies. By integrating with India’s Digital Health Ecosystem, HFR enhances accessibility, interoperability, and transparency in healthcare services. It empowers healthcare providers by ensuring their verified presence in the digital network, allowing patients and stakeholders to easily connect with registered facilities. This initiative aims to streamline healthcare delivery, improve efficiency, and create a more patient-centric, technology-driven system across the nation.
                    </p>
                </div>
